Hi Maps Team Starting Wednesday August 26 2020 at 9:00 p.m. westbound Grand Central Parkway Access Road will be temporarily closed.All vehicles wanting to access 94th Street from WB Grand Central Parkway take Exit 7 to Terminal B Departures level to the on-ramp for Runway Drive to 94th Street.All vehicles coming from Terminals C and D take 102nd Street southbound then veer right onto Ditmars Boulevard which will lead to eastbound Grand Central Parkway on-ramp and 94th Street.
